
These class files are for a probabilistic ray tracer and are
associated with the second edition of REALISTIC RAY TRACING by
Peter Shirley and R. Keith Morley (AK Peters, 2003).  These
files are in the public domain and nor warranty is implied or
given, and they should be used at your own risk.
Please send any comments or corrections to shirley@cs.utah.edu and
rmorley@cs.utah.edu

